title: A morning with Tom Daley and the GB diving team
description: Tom Daley is heading to his fourth Olympic Games as a diver for Team GB. He took Olympic bronze medals home from both London 2012 and Rio 2016. We joined Tom and diving team mates Matty Lee and Grace Reid for a quick chat.
